{"status":200,"currentLocale":"en","ranges":{"39004001-39004999":{"citation":"Malachi&nbsp;4:1-6","link":"https:\/\/www.jw.org\/en\/publications\/bible\/nwt\/books\/malachi\/4\/#v39004001-v39004006","validRange":"39004001-39004006","html":"<span class=\"verse\" id=\"v39004001\"><span class=\"style-b\"><span class=\"chapterNum\"><a href='\/en\/publications\/bible\/nwt\/books\/json\/html\/39004001-39004999#v39004001' data-anchor='#v39004001'>4 <\/a><\/span>\u00a0\u201cFor look! the day is coming, burning like a furnace,<a class=\"xrefLink jsBibleLink\" id=\"xreflink16347495\" href=\"\/en\/publications\/bible\/nwt\/books\/mcr\/16347495\/\" data-bible=\"nwt\" data-targetverses=\"36002002,61003007\">+<\/a> when all the presumptuous ones and all those practicing wickedness will become like stubble. The coming day will certainly devour them,\u201d says Jehovah of armies, \u201cand it will leave them neither root nor branch.<\/span><\/span>\n\n<span class=\"verse\" id=\"v39004002\"><span class=\"style-b\"><sup class=\"verseNum\"><a href='\/en\/publications\/bible\/nwt\/books\/json\/html\/39004001-39004999#v39004002' data-anchor='#v39004002'>2\u00a0<\/a><\/sup>\u00a0But on you who honor<a class=\"footnoteLink\" id=\"footnotesource16347518\" href='\/en\/publications\/bible\/nwt\/books\/json\/html\/39004001-39004999#fn16347518' data-anchor='#fn16347518'>*<\/a> my name, the sun of righteousness will shine, with healing in its rays;<a class=\"footnoteLink\" id=\"footnotesource16347534\" href='\/en\/publications\/bible\/nwt\/books\/json\/html\/39004001-39004999#fn16347534' data-anchor='#fn16347534'>*<\/a> and you will skip about like fattened calves.\u201d<\/span>\n<span class=\"parabreak\"><\/span><\/span>\n\n<span class=\"verse\" id=\"v39004003\"><span class=\"style-b first\"><sup class=\"verseNum\"><a href='\/en\/publications\/bible\/nwt\/books\/json\/html\/39004001-39004999#v39004003' data-anchor='#v39004003'>3\u00a0<\/a><\/sup>\u00a0\u201cAnd you will tread the wicked underfoot, for they will be like dust under the soles of your feet on the day when I take action,\u201d says Jehovah of armies.<\/span>\n<span class=\"parabreak\"><\/span><\/span>\n\n<span class=\"verse\" id=\"v39004004\"><span class=\"style-b first\"><sup class=\"verseNum\"><a href='\/en\/publications\/bible\/nwt\/books\/json\/html\/39004001-39004999#v39004004' data-anchor='#v39004004'>4\u00a0<\/a><\/sup>\u00a0\u201cRemember the Law of my servant Moses, the regulations and judgments that I commanded at Ho\u02b9reb for all Israel to obey.<a class=\"xrefLink jsBibleLink\" id=\"xreflink16347559\" href=\"\/en\/publications\/bible\/nwt\/books\/mcr\/16347559\/\" data-bible=\"nwt\" data-targetverses=\"5004005\">+<\/a><\/span>\n<span class=\"parabreak\"><\/span><\/span>\n\n<span class=\"verse\" id=\"v39004005\"><span class=\"style-b first\"><sup class=\"verseNum\"><a href='\/en\/publications\/bible\/nwt\/books\/json\/html\/39004001-39004999#v39004005' data-anchor='#v39004005'>5\u00a0<\/a><\/sup>\u00a0\u201cLook! I am sending to you E\u00b7li\u02b9jah the prophet<a class=\"xrefLink jsBibleLink\" id=\"xreflink16347582\" href=\"\/en\/publications\/bible\/nwt\/books\/mcr\/16347582\/\" data-bible=\"nwt\" data-targetverses=\"40011013-40011014,41009011-41009012\">+<\/a> before the coming of the great and awe-inspiring day of Jehovah.<a class=\"xrefLink jsBibleLink\" id=\"xreflink16347593\" href=\"\/en\/publications\/bible\/nwt\/books\/mcr\/16347593\/\" data-bible=\"nwt\" data-targetverses=\"29002031,44002020,61003010\">+<\/a><\/span><\/span>\n\n<span class=\"verse\" id=\"v39004006\"><span class=\"style-b\"><sup class=\"verseNum\"><a href='\/en\/publications\/bible\/nwt\/books\/json\/html\/39004001-39004999#v39004006' data-anchor='#v39004006'>6\u00a0<\/a><\/sup>\u00a0And he will turn the hearts of fathers back toward sons,<a class=\"xrefLink jsBibleLink\" id=\"xreflink16347615\" href=\"\/en\/publications\/bible\/nwt\/books\/mcr\/16347615\/\" data-bible=\"nwt\" data-targetverses=\"42001017\">+<\/a> and the hearts of sons back toward fathers, so that I may not come and strike the earth, devoting it to destruction.\u201d<\/span><span class=\"parabreak\"><\/span><\/span>\n\n","footnotes":"<div class=\"footnote\" id=\"fn16347518\"><a class=\"fnSourceLink\" href='\/en\/publications\/bible\/nwt\/books\/json\/html\/39004001-39004999#footnotesource16347518' data-anchor='#footnotesource16347518'>^&nbsp;<\/a><span class=\"\">Lit., \u201cfear.\u201d<\/span><\/div>\n\n<div class=\"footnote\" id=\"fn16347534\"><a class=\"fnSourceLink\" href='\/en\/publications\/bible\/nwt\/books\/json\/html\/39004001-39004999#footnotesource16347534' data-anchor='#footnotesource16347534'>^&nbsp;<\/a><span class=\"\">Lit., \u201cwings.\u201d<\/span><\/div>\n\n"}}}